    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I've spent more weekends than I can count polishing her up and making sure she stays in showroom-ready shape. This beauty has been garage-kept, pampered, and honestly looks like she just rolled off the lot. She drives as smooth as silk and turns heads at every corner. I\u2019m only letting her go to a home that will appreciate her as much as I do. Come on over, have a look, and let\u2019s talk cars\u2014you won't find another one this clean!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered platform. This unit has been curated with a zero-compromise approach to mechanical integrity. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a perfectly indexed valvetrain, with a recent VANOS overhaul using Besian systems to ensure optimal cam timing and zero rattle. Rod bearings have been proactively addressed with treated shells for bottom-end security. The chassis is exceptionally rigid, having undergone full subframe reinforcement to handle lateral g-loads without fatigue. Compression across all cylinders remains within a 2% delta, confirming a robust combustion seal and factory-spec power delivery. The factory finish retains incredible depth, and the suspension geometry has been precision-aligned for neutral turn-in. This is a turnkey, apex-ready machine for the enthusiast who demands a zero-tolerance fitment and peerless drivetrain response.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
