    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine draped in midnight silk. Imagine the gentle purr of the engine as you glide through the mist of a Saturday morning, the hand-stitched leather embracing you like a long-lost memory. Every curve of its unblemished silhouette tells a story of elegance and unyielding spirit. It\u2019s a masterpiece that demands to be driven, a rare jewel that turns every mundane commute into a grand tour across the Riviera. To own this is to possess a piece of history that still breathes with the vitality of its first day on the road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
