    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives so smoothly you\u2019ll forget you\u2019re even on the road! There\u2019s barely a speck on her, and she\u2019s been treated with nothing but love. I\u2019m only letting her go to make some room in the garage for a new project, and I\u2019d truly love for her to go to someone who will appreciate her as much as I have. Come by, let's chat cars, and get you behind the wheel of your dream ride!",
      "price": 44900.0,
