    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level specimen for the discerning purist. This chassis has been maintained with surgical precision, featuring a power plant that exhibits optimal compression across all cylinders with zero parasitic loss. We\u2019ve addressed the common failure points with reinforced bushings and a recalibrated induction system for peak volumetric efficiency. The gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement with perfectly indexed synchros, and the suspension geometry has been dialed to eliminate any hint of lateral deflection. This is a turn-key machine with a pristine undercarriage and a service history that reflects a total commitment to mechanical integrity. If you demand a vehicle where the throttle response is instantaneous and the handling is telepathic, this is your apex predator.",
